*Crkva* se nalazi u centru grada. (The church is located in the city center.)

*Crkvu* su gradili preko dve decenije. (They were building the church for over two decades.)

Ljudi su oduvek imali poštovanja prema *crkvi*. (People have always had respect for the church.)

Mnogi ljudi vole da posete *crkve* u drugim zemljama. (Many people like to visit churches in other countries.)

Vladika je održao propoved u *crkvi*. (The bishop held a sermon in the church.)